Instagram post by @noorie_rai, 16 September 2018. Artistic painting of temple bells with red cloth/dupatta. Text overlaid: 'Noor' (top left), 'Shakti' (right), 'Adi' (lower left), '16-09-2018' (date). Fiery orange/yellow tones. 'Adi Shakti' = primordial cosmic energy. 'Noor' = divine light. Date sum: 1+6+0+9+2+0+1+8=27, 2+7=9. Temple bells = cosmic calling. Red dupatta = Shakti. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Avatar Declaration — declaring herself as Adi Shakti (Primordial Energy) and Noor (Divine Light).